# Queue Features

This directory contains Gherkin feature files for Queue and Deque interface examples.

## Planned Features

- PriorityQueue (natural ordering, Comparator)
- ArrayDeque (Stack and Queue operations)
- LinkedList as Deque

## Structure

Each feature file should follow the pattern:
```
# language: es

Característica: [Feature description]
  Como desarrollador Java
  Quiero [objective]
  Para [benefit]

  Escenario: [Scenario description]
    Dado [precondition]
    Cuando [action]
    Entonces [expected result]
```

## Notes

- All features should be written in neutral Spanish
- Demonstrate FIFO (Queue) and LIFO (Stack) behaviors
- Show differences between Queue implementations
